Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在大地震届满6周年的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各地正举行各种悼念祭来…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 连杆上有裂纹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没拿去店里修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要修理引擎的话 已经没那么多社团经费了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台是自己组装的机器 所以想自己修修看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}接下来是关于政治与经济的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GGP治安维持部队的最高负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(30,280)}GGP治安维持部队\N新司令官 今日上任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}罗曼洛夫·卡连巴古大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子上收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有社团活动 我为了不忘记…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的比赛后 感觉好像发现了什么灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Rideback的骑术又或者是自我真实能力展现的方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 琳 你还记得今天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是站前商场举行大甩卖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说好跟你一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的 搭档 别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就先去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是好高兴呢 琳找到了能让自己如此专注的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那不是Rideback吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}…计划投入警察部队的特殊车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}通称的“白Ride” 首次对媒体公开发表了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\fs22}“白Ride”:为了理解我们之后也会翻为“警用Rideback”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(40,290)}警察特殊车辆“白Ride”对媒体发表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:46.73,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:46.73,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:48.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:48.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:58.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:30.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:42.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:42.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:45.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:56.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
